At the same time, you thought it appropriate to include the name +Nouveau center+, with the slogan +UDF of today+, on your promotional materials and on the welcome website of your movement.
As you know, you have no right to use this abbreviation, explains the UDF committee, which asks the NC movement to "immediately remove all mention of the UDF name from all promotional materials, including (its) website".
At the same time, he asks Hervé de Charette "to hand over trademark ownership to legitimate owners".
